---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<section>
				<h1>AI Program Delivery, Governance, and Secure Adoption for Enterprise Systems</h1>
				<p>
					Organizations are rapidly adopting AI tools such as ChatGPT and Microsoft Copilot, often without clear ownership, governance, or execution structure.
				</p>
				<p>
					lisAIconsulting helps enterprise teams not only assess AI risk, but <b> plan, govern, and execute AI adoption initiatives across business and technology organizations.</b>
				</p>
				<p>
					<a href="/contact">Request an AI Risk Assessment</a>
				</p>
			</section>

			<section id="services">
				<h2>Services</h2>
<h3>AI Program &amp; Delivery Leadership</h3>
				<ul>
					Lead cross-functional AI initiatives from planning through execution
				</u>
<ul>
					Coordinate business, engineering, security, and compliance stakeholders
				</u>
<ul>
					Manage dependencies, risks, and delivery timelines
				</u>
<ul>
					Establish governance and operating models aligned to execution
				</u>

				<h3>AI Privacy &amp; Risk Assessment</h3>
				<p>
					Identify where sensitive data may be exposed across AI tools, internal workflows, and
					user practices. Assess current-state risk and provide prioritized recommendations.
				</p>

				<h3>GPT &amp; Copilot Readiness Review</h3>
				<p>
					Evaluate whether your organization is ready to deploy AI tools responsibly, including
					permissions, data access, governance, and usage patterns.
				</p>

				<h3>AI Governance &amp; Secure Adoption Advisory</h3>
				<p>
					Define practical policies, guardrails, and operating models that support AI adoption while
					maintaining privacy, compliance, and business control.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2>Why lisAIconsulting</h2>
				<p>
					Lisa Canter brings more than 20 years of experience leading enterprise technology programs
					across regulated and high-accountability environments.
				</p>
				<ul>
					<li>Healthcare IT and secure data exchange</li>
					<li>Medical device and quality/compliance environments</li>
					<li>State government AI rollout and enterprise enablement</li>
					<li>Cross-functional program delivery across business and technical teams</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2>Sample Engagement</h2>
				<h3>AI Privacy &amp; Security Assessment</h3>
				<p>
					A focused assessment designed to help organizations understand where AI usage creates
					privacy, data handling, and governance risk.
				</p>
				<ul>
					<li>Review current AI tools and usage scenarios</li>
					<li>Identify sensitive data exposure risks</li>
					<li>Assess governance and control gaps</li>
					<li>Deliver a prioritized risk summary and recommendations</li>
				</ul>
				<p>
					<a href="/demo">View Sample Output</a>
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2>Who This Helps</h2>
				<ul>
					<li>Healthcare organizations evaluating AI use with sensitive data</li>
					<li>Government teams balancing innovation with policy and control</li>
					<li>Enterprise leaders seeking safer AI adoption and clearer guardrails</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2>Start with a Practical Risk Review</h2>
				<p>
					If your organization is using AI tools and needs a clearer view of privacy, governance,
					and adoption risk, lisAIconsulting can help.
				</p>
				<p>
					<a href="/contact">Schedule a Consultation</a>
				</p>
			</section>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
